Who are you, little girl?

24
00:01:44,900 --> 00:01:47,000
Smelly Xiao Fei,

25
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:48,400
stop adding random improvisations.

26
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:50,800
Hey, why are you crying?

27
