32
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:03,300
That's Xiao Jiang.

33
00:02:03,300 --> 00:02:05,700
He's scaring little children again.

34
00:02:05,700 --> 00:02:07,300
He isn't a weird man, little girl.

35
