This place hasn't been cleaned for a long time.

41
00:02:21,200 --> 00:02:23,300
My goodness.

42
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:28,800
Oh, dear. There's even a skeleton.

43
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:31,900
Is this really a place for humans to live?

44
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:39,700
It stinks. It stinks.

45
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:45,800
There's definitely a lot of cockroaches and rats.

46
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:47,800
Yo Yo, do you really live here?

47
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:49,700
Yes.

48
