80
00:04:16,300 --> 00:04:18,300
We'll need to set a time.

81
00:04:18,300 --> 00:04:19,700
Did you know?

82
00:04:19,700 --> 00:04:23,500
The professor from the Life and Death Studies Department left early to give birth prematurely.

83
00:04:23,500 --> 00:04:25,900
Premature birth? Really?

84
00:04:25,900 --> 00:04:27,600
Then who's the substitute professor this time?

85
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:31,000
I think it's Death Note from the Anthropology Department.

86
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:32,000
Death Note?

87
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:32,500
Who's that?

88
00:04:32,500 --> 00:04:34,800
Students!

89
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:37,400
Those who should leave, leave. Those who want to stay, stay.

90
00:04:37,400 --> 00:04:42,400
Once I begin the lesson, nobody gets to leave until the bell rings.

91
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:45,900
