92
00:04:45,900 --> 00:04:48,700
I will be taking over her class for the next two months.

93
00:04:51,300 --> 00:04:54,100
Xiao Fei, isn't he...

94
00:04:55,200 --> 00:04:57,700
Wow. He had a complete "face over."

95
00:04:57,700 --> 00:04:59,200
Yes.

96
00:05:01,900 --> 00:05:05,200
My surname is Shi. "Shi" as in "right" from right or wrong.

97
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:07,300
Shi Yi Jie.

98
00:05:07,300 --> 00:05:08,900
Some of you have taken my class before,

99
00:05:08,900 --> 00:05:10,800
