125
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:05,800
Yo Yo, wake up.

126
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:06,500
Don't sleep any longer.

127
00:07:06,500 --> 00:07:07,600
No!

128
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:09,700
